{"tid":717444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大鑊了！特朗普民望首逾50%　新興市場危機恐惡化","createTime":"2018-06-26T04:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T06:40:18.000Z","uid":5812,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"40c75143f24c11987959af8cbd3bfdcc65049b8c","tid":717444,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，全美經濟調查(All-America Economic Survey)發表民調顯示，美國總統特朗普自2016年11月當選以來，民望首次超過50%！反映其經濟政策及整體工作表現獲得民眾支持。 <br />\n<br />\n調查顯示，特朗普最新民望爆升6個百分點，達51%；反對他的僅36%，較3月下跌6個百分點。相比今年首季，他的民望僅41%；對他不滿的人高達47%。換句話說，特朗普在處理貿易及移民政策問題上沒有造成民眾十分不滿的情況。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，這對於新興市場來說是噩耗，皆因美元與特朗普支持度相關度甚高！回顧往績，若他在過去兩個月民望上升，美元就會經歷大幅上漲，通常是滯後民望約45天。(本文附圖) <br />\n<br />\n曾有分析表示，若以往績推算，假若特朗普民望升至超過47%(目前已一舉升穿)，美元更有機會展開大升浪，即由目前至45天左右之後，會看到美元更強。一旦如此，新興市場危機恐加劇。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國贏"},{"pid":"55cf1cc5550910aadf935af3f6fe9b8f51399317","tid":717444,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:57:52.000Z","msg":"阿根廷同土耳其會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf256b0f3056187ec5473b225638ba0bf22e9b4","tid":717444,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55cf1cc5550910aadf935af3f6fe9b8f51399317","tid":717444,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:57:52.000Z","msg":"阿根廷同土耳其會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cac8e49084eae7892ca27431ae46e4e90102756","tid":717444,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:31:03.000Z","msg":"美元快D 升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12892fb2aba97d98281a7513fe63af6176923b57","tid":717444,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:40:18.000Z","msg":"人仔已經跌左好多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}